headline: Intuit Hosts Investor Day, Reaffirms First-Quarter and Fiscal 2026 Guidance
summary: MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif., September 18, 2025--Intuit Inc. (Nasdaq: INTU), the global financial technology platform that makes Intuit TurboTax, Credit Karma, QuickBooks, and Mailchimp, reaffirmed its financial guidance for the first quarter and full fiscal year 2026 in conjunction with its Investor Day. The event is being held today at the company's Mountain View, CA headquarters and begins at 8:00 a.m. PT.
